CREATE TABLE `bigquery-public-data.geo_us_roads.all_roads_50`
(
  road_geom GEOGRAPHY OPTIONS(description="Geographic representation of the road. Each road is a line string. Primary roads will have two separate rows with different geographies representing each direction of travel"),
  road_id STRING OPTIONS(description="Unique identifier for each road"),
  full_name STRING OPTIONS(description="Full text name of the road"),
  route_type STRING OPTIONS(description="Defines the route type for a given road. Possible values: C - County; I - Interstate; M - Common Name; O - Other; S - State-Recognized; U - U.S."),
  mtfcc_feature_class_code STRING OPTIONS(description="MAF/TIGER feature class code. Maps to `bigquery-public-data.census_utility.mtfcc_feature_class_codes`")
);

CREATE TABLE `bigquery-public-data.geo_us_roads.us_national_roads`
(
  road_id STRING,
  full_name STRING,
  route_type STRING,
  mtfcc_feature_class_code STRING,
  state_fips_code INT64,
  state_name STRING,
  road_geom GEOGRAPHY
)
PARTITION BY DATE(_PARTITIONTIME)
CLUSTER BY state_name, state_fips_code, route_type, full_name;
